data.description: Super cute 3 bedroom 2 bath patio home with easy access to schools, parks and shopping! Kitchen opens to the dining and living and has a lovely skylight!  Fabulous features include high ceilings, tile flooring, carpeting in bedrooms only and wood shutters!  Master bedroom has a large bathroom, separate shower and tub, 2 sinks/vanities, large closet and private access to the backyard. Backyard has 7' fence on concrete perimeter and wrought iron gates! This is the perfect low maintenance home!
